                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="315329" author="koutoupis" created="Tue, 12 Oct 2021 19:26:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@Andreas Dilger, I spoke with my team and they provided me with the history on why it was part of our configuration and why it may not have been immediately removed. Thank you for your input. I will close this issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="315316" author="adilger" created="Tue, 12 Oct 2021 16:47:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This attribute has done nothing since Lustre 2.1, according to my &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13326&quot; title=&quot;remove MDS_SETATTR_PORTAL on MDS&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13326&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13326&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch that removes it.  Was there a reason this module parameter was being used?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Typically I&apos;m on the side of maintaining compatibility, but this is totally safe to remove from the 2.12 LTS system before the upgrade without any loss of functionality, so I&apos;m not sure what benefit there would be to keeping compatibility?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
